{"tid":970523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普說乘中國經濟疲軟美國談判佔優勢","createTime":"2019-01-06T01:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T15:10:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"78e053155013a00497f510c432b34d65e7414ccc","tid":970523,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"特朗普說乘中國經濟疲軟美國談判佔優勢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190105-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%AA%AA%E4%B9%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E4%BD%94%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190105-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E4%25B9%2598%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E7%2596%25B2%25E8%25BB%259F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%2588%25A4%25E4%25BD%2594%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%258B%25A2&d=ew77jXDyOYNVIOodbIO3mKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d8f9ccb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190105-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%AA%AA%E4%B9%98%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E4%BD%94%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周五表示，因當前中國經濟疲軟，美國可以從與中國的貿易談判中獲得一些好處。特朗普還對關於與中國的貿易磋商稱 &ldquo;期待達成協議，如果無法達成協議他們將支付巨額關稅&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道，美國總統特朗普稱中國經濟疲軟使美國在貿易磋商中佔優勢。特朗普周五表示，因當前中國經濟疲軟，美國可以從與中國的貿易談判中獲得一些好處。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據特朗普說，&ldquo;我告訴你，現在中國經濟表現不佳，這使我們處於非常有利的地位。我們的經濟狀況非常強勁，&rdquo;特朗普在白宮玫瑰園發表講話時說，&ldquo;我認為我們將與中國達成協議，我真的認為他們想要達成協議，我認為他們不得不這麼做。&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n據共同社今天報道，美國總統特朗普4日在白宮舉行記者會，關於與中國的貿易磋商據特朗普稱 &ldquo;期待達成協議，如果無法達成協議他們將支付巨額關稅&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室（USTR）副代表格里什和財政部副部長馬爾帕斯等組成的代表團將訪華並於7日起展開貿易磋商，農業部、商務部和能源部的負責人也將同行。特朗普還稱：&ldquo;我認為他們希望達成協議，且應該必須達成協議。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n圍繞美國蘋果公司因在中國銷售低迷而下調了業績預期一事，特朗普強調：&ldquo;蘋果在中國製造產品，中國是最大的受益者。我希望iPhone在美國生產。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"63c74f36e5223132bab0ae48844c64830a7849b6","tid":970523,"uid":57376,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:44:19.000Z","msg":"一個文革出生小學生又點會夠商場歷練幾十年嘅生意佬鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4015d013f26c7e510f59d98f4c09e2fdd8b02c6","tid":970523,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c74fe7d2c28a0308ed9c31d889f93095687f3b","tid":970523,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a06055fa1899310380fd9e0d6cc626a27ca5a3aa","tid":970523,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"爭咩啫<br />\n<br />\npmi鬥跌得快囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b682d5ae235607c9a6f5441f5c667f358b9a21f2","tid":970523,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18160b00159aabac6472f8383e7204cd6b048d50","tid":970523,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c74f36e5223132bab0ae48844c64830a7849b6","tid":970523,"uid":57376,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:44:19.000Z","msg":"一個文革出生小學生又點會夠商場歷練幾十年嘅生意佬鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"一個經濟大國<br />\n點夠一個農業加工業加經濟加軍事國鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581962dfe7415dd1365f35054d370e60625544a9","tid":970523,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T11:02:05.0